FBIS3-25320 "drafr031_d_94008" FBIS-AFR-94-031 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Feb 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Malawi Banda Selected as MCP Candidate for President EA1302213994 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network in English 1800 GMT 13 Feb 94 EA1302213994 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] At the ongoing [word indistinct] Malawi Congress Party, [MCP], convention, His Excellency Ngwazi [paramount] Dr. Kamuzu Banda, has been voted as the party's presidential candidate in the forthcoming presidential elections. Our correspondent said the Honorable Gwanda Chakuamba is his vice [president]. The convention is still in session.
